Q. What is the output for the following?

   public class Test {
      public static void main(String [] args) {
         short a, b, c=0;
         a=1;
         b=2;
         c=a+b;
         System.out.println(c);
      }
  }

1). Compile error.
2). 3
3). 1
4). runtime exception
Solution :
option [1] is correct
Attempted :
option [1] is attempted
